Module slogo_team01

Package view.mainpane

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    MainPane
    Interface representing a main pane object that contains the basic views required for any slogo simulation.
    SelectorPaneObserver
    Interface for a Selector Pane observer, that should be updated whenever the selector pane changes state.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    ControlPaneElement
    Represents each individual pane element in the control visualiser, containing both the actual interactive pane and a label showing the name of the pane.
    ControlVisualiser
    Control Visualiser class containing the stage that contains all possible additional panes that user can interact with.
    MainPaneConstants
    Class containing constants for classes in the mainpane package.
    MainVisualiser
    Main Visualiser class storing the turtle pane and the selector pane.
    PaneProperties
    A container used to contain and set necessary properties of a pane in the main pane.
